Package: LearningWithExternalStats
Title: Machine learning algorithms that exploit external statistics in addition to internal data
Version: 0.0.3
Authors@R: 
    person("Tal", "El Hay", , "talelh@kinstitute.org.il", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2156-1558"))
Description: Currently the package focuses on evaluation performance of a model in an external dataset using internal data and statsitics from the external dataset. The core function reweights the internal data to have statistics that match the external statistics.
